<br>
Your pet will be dead, the SG at about 50% health, and you'll be around 40% mana.<br>
<br>
SGs hit for around 90-100pts of damage a whack.  They have about 2500-3000hps.<br>
<br>
I'm beginning to doubt that a 40 mage could consistantly solo an SG.  In any case, good luck in your attempt.  Be sure to have a SoW in case it goes badly.<br>
