<br>
The first time, pet lived with about 10% health left.  Used 5 Cinder bolts.  Giant started to charge me on the third or fourth bolt, but he turned around in the face of all that incoming fire (I loved it).  All bolts hit for 333 damage.<br>
<br>
The second time, pet lived with about 30% health and I used 4 Cinder bolts.  Obviously a weaker giant.  Again, all bolts hit for 333.<br>
<br>
